=head1 NAME

NIGHT_LOG_LONG - creates a text log detailing file headers.

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This recipe does the same as the NIGHT_LOG recipe, except that it
produces a more detailed log.

=head1 SEE ALSO

The spectroscopy recipe: NIGHT_LOG
The spectroscopy primitive: _NIGHT_LOG_

